	&amp;quot;We wanted to provide a more valuable interactive experience for both new and loyal Channellock customers,&amp;quot; said Ryan DeArment, vice president of sales and marketing at Channellock. &amp;quot;The new site celebrates our tool heritage, people and commitment to quality.&amp;quot;&lt;br /&gt;
